text: Tuhan boh miseu keu ureueng mukmin Inong Peuraʻun nyang that meutuah Geukheun Tuhanku Neupeugot rumoh Keu lon nyo saboh Neubri hadiyah Dalam churuga Neupeugot keu lon Lom Neupeuglah lon bak kaphe jadah Neupeuglah lon nyoe nibak Peuraʻun Ngon buet jih nyan dum raya that salah Neupeuglah lon bak kawom nyang lalem
